ATHENIA STEEL COMPANY, Plaintiff In Error, v. Frank K. BOWERS, as Collector, etc., Defendant in Error. (Circuit Court of Appeals, Second Circuit. November 11, 1926.) No. 95. Geo. W. Bristol and Walter H. Dodd, both of New York City, for plaintiff in error. Emory R. Buckner, U. S. Atty., of New York City (Edw. Feldman, Asst. U. S. Atty., of New York City, of counsel), for defendant in error.

Before HOUGH, HAND, and MACK, Circuit Judges.

PER CURIAM.

Judgment affirmed in open court.
